trans-unit.source: Represents an editable content region within the design-time markup for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en redigerbare innhold området i utformingen markup for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the EditableDesignerRegion class to help manage templates at design time.
trans-unit.target: Bruk EditableDesignerRegion klassen for å administrere maler under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> will use an instance of this class with its <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> method to generate HTML markup of the region's content.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>bruker en forekomst av denne klassen med den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A>metode for å generere HTML-kode på det området innhold.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> class using the given owner and name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte eier og navn.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"></xref> object, or a designer that derives from <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"> </xref> -objekt eller en designer som er avledet fra <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> class using the given owner and name and the initial value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion.ServerControlsOnly*> property.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte eieren og navnet og startverdien for de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion.ServerControlsOnly*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion.ServerControlsOnly*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"></xref> object, or a designer that derives from <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"> </xref> -objekt eller en designer som er avledet fra <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to have the region accept only Web server controls for content; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>er område godtar bare server webkontroller for innhold. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the HTML markup for the content of the region.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir HTML-koden for innholdet på området.

trans-unit.source: HTML markup representing the content of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: HTML-kode som representerer innholdet i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewRendering"></xref> object containing the design-time HTML markup for the given control.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewRendering"> </xref> objektet som inneholder utformingen HTML-koden for kontrollen som er angitt.

trans-unit.source: The control for which to get the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewRendering"></xref> object for the current region.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen å få den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewRendering"> </xref> objekt for gjeldende område.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the region can accept only Web server controls.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om området godtar bare webkontroller server.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the region can contain only Web server controls; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis området kan inneholde bare server webkontroller; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the region can be bound to a data source.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om området kan være bundet til en datakilde.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> content supports binding to a data source; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> innhold støtter binding til en datakilde; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
